OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772136279
OL,3,CUp to 600 jobs to be cut at Aston
OL,4,CMartin as annual losses widen
OL,6,FAston Martin, which is based in
OL,7,FWarwickshire, is cutting up to nearly
OL,8,F600 jobs across their global workforce.
OL,10,FThe luxury car maker confirmed plans
OL,11,Fto axe up to 20% of workers, after
OL,12,Fseeing annual losses widen.
OL,14,FIt employs 2,800 people, and the
OL,15,Flatest job losses follow 170 job cuts
OL,16,Fthat were announced at the start of
OL,17,Flast year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772136279
OL,3,CUp to 600 jobs to be cut at Aston
OL,4,CMartin as annual losses widen
OL,6,FThe group, which is consulting on the
OL,7,Flatest redundancy programme, said it
OL,8,Fwould reduce its global workforce by
OL,9,Fup to another fifth.
OL,11,F"Difficult decision"
OL,13,FAston Martin said: "Having undertaken
OL,14,Fat the start of 2025 a process to make
OL,15,Forganisational adjustments to ensure
OL,16,Fthe business was appropriately
OL,17,Fresourced for its future plans, we had
OL,18,Fto take the difficult decision at the
OL,19,Fend of 2025 to implement further
OL,20,Fchanges.
OL,26,@uD@TOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772136279
OL,3,CUp to 600 jobs to be cut at Aston
OL,4,CMartin as annual losses widen
OL,6,F"This latest programme will ultimately
OL,7,Fsee the departure of up to 20% of our
OL,8,Fvalued workforce."
OL,10,FThe group said the redundancies are as
OL,11,Fpart of plans to cut costs by around
OL,12,F#40 million, most of which would be
OL,13,Fstripped out this year.
OL,15,FIt's understood that most of the cuts
OL,16,Fwill impact the UK operations, where
OL,17,Fthe majority of Aston Martin's workers
OL,18,Fare based.
OL,20,FRoles across the business will be
OL,21,Fimpacted, including factory staff.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772136279
OL,3,CUp to 600 jobs to be cut at Aston
OL,4,CMartin as annual losses widen
OL,6,FThe group's employees were told about
OL,7,Fthe job cut programme at the end of
OL,8,Flast year.
OL,10,FUS tariff hikes and weak demand
OL,12,FAston Martin also has a site in St
OL,13,FAthan in Wales, as well as worldwide
OL,14,Foffices and dealerships.
OL,16,FAnnual results from the firm revealed
OL,17,Fwidened pre-tax losses of #363.9
OL,18,Fmillion for 2025 against losses of
OL,19,F#289.1 million the previous year, as
OL,20,Ftrading came under pressure from US
OL,21,Ftariff hikes and weak demand.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772136279
OL,3,CUp to 600 jobs to be cut at Aston
OL,4,CMartin as annual losses widen
OL,6,FThe car manufacturer warned last week
OL,7,Fof worse-than-expected profits for
OL,8,F2025 on the back of falling sales as
OL,9,Fit battles pressure from US tariffs.
OL,11,FIt revealed total wholesale sales by
OL,12,Fvolume dropped 10% to 5,448 in 2025.
OL,14,FThe US is the car maker's largest
OL,15,Fmarket but it was hit by a 10% tariff
OL,16,Flast year, reduced from a previously
OL,17,Fplanned 27.5%.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
