CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772136279
OL,3,CUp to 600 jobs to be cut at Aston
OL,4,CMartin as annual losses widen
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe company has taken action to help
OL,12,Fboost its finances, including cutting
OL,13,Finvestment plans last October.
OL,15,FLast week it also revealed a deal to
OL,16,Fsell the naming rights to its Aston
OL,17,FMartin F1 Team to related party AMR GP
OL,18,FHoldings for #50 million.
OL,20,F"A highly challenging trading
OL,21,Fenvironment"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
