OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772136279
OL,3,CUp to 600 jobs to be cut at Aston
OL,4,CMartin as annual losses widen
OL,6,FAdrian Hallmark, Aston Martin Chief
OL,7,FExecutive, said:
OL,9,F"In 2025, we navigated a highly
OL,10,Fchallenging trading environment whilst
OL,11,Fdelivering on critical operational
OL,12,Fmilestones.
OL,14,F"An unprecedented backdrop of
OL,15,Fgeopolitical uncertainties and
OL,16,Fmacroeconomic pressures, including
OL,17,Fheightened tariffs in the US and
OL,18,FChina, weighed on our performance and
OL,19,Fability to execute our plans
OL,20,Feffectively."
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772136279
OL,3,CUp to 600 jobs to be cut at Aston
OL,4,CMartin as annual losses widen
OL,6,FHe added the year ahead was set to see
OL,7,Fa "a material improvement in financial
OL,8,Fperformance", but said tariffs remain
OL,9,Fa headache for the firm.
OL,11,FHe said: "The group continues to
OL,12,Fengage with both the US and UK
OL,13,Fgovernments to secure greater clarity
OL,14,Fand certainty on the specific
OL,15,Fautomotive tariff.
OL,26,@oD@COUpD@LO]sD@JOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772136279
OL,3,CUp to 600 jobs to be cut at Aston
OL,4,CMartin as annual losses widen
OL,6,F"Whilst positive dialogue on this
OL,7,Fmatter has been achieved directly with
OL,8,Fthe US government, the company
OL,9,Fcontinues to seek more proactive
OL,10,Fsupport from the UK Government to
OL,11,Fprotect the interests of small volume
OL,12,Fmanufacturers, like Aston Martin, who
OL,13,Fprovide thousands of jobs, making an
OL,14,Fimportant contribution to local
OL,15,Feconomies and to the wider UK
OL,16,Fautomotive supply chain."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@YO]
